ZH: 我明天要穿上新衣服去上班。
EN: I will wear new clothes to work tomorrow.

ZH: 你应该穿上合适的服装去参加晚宴。
EN: You should wear appropriate clothing to attend the dinner party.

ZH: 她穿上一件漂亮的裙子去参加派对。
EN: She wore a beautiful dress to the party.

ZH: 我们决定穿上运动服去徒步旅行。
EN: We decided to wear sportswear for hiking.

ZH: 在冷天气里，要穿上保暖的羽绒服。
EN: In cold weather, wear a warm down jacket.

ZH: 穿上毛衣会更暖和。
EN: It will be warmer if you wear a sweater.

ZH: 她穿上高跟鞋去参加聚会。
EN: She wore high heels to the gathering.

ZH: 他穿上西装去参加婚礼。
EN: He wore a suit to attend the wedding.

ZH: 小孩子们穿上凉鞋去海边玩耍。
EN: The children put on sandals to play by the sea.

ZH: 我经常穿上运动装去健身房。
EN: I often wear sportswear to the gym.

ZH: 她喜欢穿上长裙去参加舞会。
EN: She likes to wear long dresses to attend parties.

ZH: 在夏天，最舒服的着装是穿上短裤。
EN: The most comfortable outfit in summer is to wear shorts.

ZH: 他决定穿上便装去参加聚会。
EN: He decided to wear casual clothes to the gathering.

ZH: 你应该穿上耐克鞋去运动。
EN: You should wear Nike shoes for sports.

ZH: 她穿上外套以应对寒冷天气。
EN: She put on a jacket to cope with the cold weather.

ZH: 在结婚典礼上，新娘要穿上白色的婚纱。
EN: The bride should wear a white wedding dress at the wedding ceremony.

ZH: 我们都穿上了敬业的制服。
EN: We all put on professional uniforms.

ZH: 孩子们奔跑着穿上了尖头鞋。
EN: The children ran around wearing pointed shoes.

ZH: 看起来她穿上了一条新裙子。
EN: It looks like she is wearing a new skirt. 

ZH: 明天会下雨，所以记得穿上雨衣。
EN: It will rain tomorrow, so remember to wear a raincoat.
